{"id":"gregory.sh-yb9","title":"Automate SEO with AI/LLM pipeline","description":"Build an automated pipeline that uses AI/LLMs to handle SEO tasks:\n\n**Auto-generation:**\n- Generate meta descriptions from post content if not provided\n- Suggest/generate OG images based on post title and content\n- Auto-generate alt text for images in posts\n\n**Optimization:**\n- Analyze posts for SEO improvements (keyword density, readability, headers)\n- Suggest internal linking opportunities between posts\n- Generate structured data (JSON-LD) for articles\n\n**Monitoring:**\n- Track Lighthouse scores over time\n- Alert on SEO regressions (missing meta, broken links, etc.)\n\n**Implementation ideas:**\n- Pre-commit hook or build step that runs LLM analysis\n- Could use Claude API or local models\n- Store suggestions as PR comments or build warnings","status":"open","priority":3,"issue_type":"feature","owner":"theo@gregory.sh","created_at":"2026-02-09T16:24:33.200115+01:00","created_by":"Theo Gregory","updated_at":"2026-02-09T16:24:33.200115+01:00"}
